These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, bus, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bus | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, woodworking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
House: art-deco, colonial, cottage
1. the colonial house is in an even position##4
2. the colonial house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
3. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| House   | art-deco | colonial | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, subway, boat
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Transport   | car | boat | subway |

