.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, electronic
1. the fan of electronic is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of salsa is the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | salsa | electronic |

