.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday   | june | january | september |

 